message.entry: Brace indexing into a lazy colon descriptor is not supported.
Indexing into an empty colon descriptor is not supported.
The method {0} is not supported for lazy colon descriptor.
Only one index to a lazy colon descriptor is supported.
Combining lazy colon indexing with parenReference is not supported.
Assignment to elements of a lazy colon descriptor is not supported.
Single precision index values must be less than 2^24.
Index value must be less than 2^53.
